{"tid":9130,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[ios/an/web]lihkg bugs 集中回報區","createTime":"2016-11-28T13:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T03:56:14.000Z","uid":2107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa48d06642d0bdbbe2dfd0ce59b1b79834e8389","tid":9130,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"我見an機 入埋黎之後都出現一d 新bugs <br />\n所以開個bug回報區討論下 方便admin 做野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwcF122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwcF122.jpg&h=462ae704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.icon 我本來係打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但人地quote變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/214948_0c26ae751982bb373ab3bfae8911c101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F214948_0c26ae751982bb373ab3bfae8911c101.jpg&h=f1708c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.時間有null 同1970年<br />\n<br />\n3.禁回帶個時睇完紅點個post 再禁多次粒紅點又出 但個post 無最新留言<br />\n<br />\n4.有時右邊個頁數List 同 post 唔一致<br />\n<br />\n5.試過幾時彈app <br />\n<br />\n6. 我朋友話an 版無得唔自動下載圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望admin 見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申6s+ 10.1.1"},{"pid":"1f2ab2c7b05382170e81e13f0cacbb9800da8d0f","tid":9130,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fa44fb14f2fca08d05500a6a9643fd21c8953729","tid":9130,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"自己回完post出去f5有紅點 入番去最新都係得自己個reply"},{"pid":"482d8ed49c905890ddbeb56c765f1ad5c68fdf7a","tid":9130,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己回完post出去f5有紅點 入番去最新都係得自己個reply</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 有時想追post 都幾煩"},{"pid":"dca1257d1dbb8f92367fa5